Presidente Roque Sáenz Peña Department is a  department of Córdoba Province in Argentina.
The provincial subdivision has a population of about 34,647 inhabitants in an area of 8,228 km2, and its capital city is Laboulaye, which is located around 520 km from Capital Federal.
